{"tid":1597936,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我呀媽話冇權用啲錢，我可以講咩好？","createTime":"2019-09-27T07:35:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T07:37:56.000Z","uid":43083,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"305e10a239c5d60180fd5193e871e40ffa2d9281","tid":1597936,"uid":43083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:35:11.000Z","msg":"20年前，我呀爺俾咗一筆錢俾我「呀媽」去用，仲同佢講：「你想點用就點用啦，我唔會理你」<br />\n咁我呀媽又真係亂咁用啲錢，<br />\n咁三個月前，我就同我「呀媽」講，我有五樣嘢要買<br />\n我「呀媽」不停拒絕，話晒錢，唔買得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我咪嗰嗰星期都同我「呀媽」講「五樣物品，缺一不可」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然佢係買咗一樣，咁但仲有四樣嘢未買喎<br />\n就喺琴晚，我呀媽同我講：「一筆錢，兩個人用。如果我買咗比你，呀爺就會唔開心！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但明明就話我「呀媽」有權可以用筆錢<br />\n<br />\n我可以點同我「呀媽」解釋？<br />\n我諗緊我係咪佢親生?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，我有同住樓上嗰個講英文嘅叔叔講咗依件事！但我呀叔又話依件係我地嘅家事，唔關你事！<br />\n<br />\n點搞好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9feca79788e205e71e719f06fdffa67e34cb147e","tid":1597936,"uid":94968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:37:56.000Z","msg":"咩呀叔呀 明明就係親生老豆"}]}